name: Syndicate Choppers Lower Leg Shaving Service
description:
Syndicate Choppers offers lower leg shaving on any style of lower legs you have.
Pricing is for a set of legs.
Powdercoating is available for an additional $35 per set.
Please specify color of powder you want.

We can shave off all fender tabs and brake tabs or just the fender whichever you prefer.

Send us your lowers and we will shave them for you.

name: Syndicate Choppers Custom Exhausts
description:
Syndicate Choppers custom exhausts done for most type of Harley Davidson motors. Basic types of exhaust start at $650 for mild steel and go up based on design and material used.
The style of Evo Sportster Exhaust Shown here are $650 as well as most type of "shotgun" "hi and lows" and high and tights" designs.
Please contact us at blkstang0321@yahoo.com and tell us what type of bike they are going on and what ideas you might have and we will get it sorted out and get a great custom design to what you want on your bike.

name: Syndicate Choppers Custom Handlebars For Use Without Risers
description:
Custom Handlebar Designs for use without risers 
please specify what style of bars you want and measurements.

"Tall and Narrow Bars" are shown in the picture but we offer many more styles of bars like "T-Bars" "Look Through Bars", etc.

If you are unsure or what you want or have some ideas please email us at blkstang0321@yahoo.com and we will help you out with your needs and get the right style custom handlebar you are looking for.

Available in 1" or 7/8" outside diameters
All of our custom handlebars are made of quality made in the USA with .120 wall thick tubing. 
Raw steel available
304 grade stainless steel also available

All of our riser less custom handlebars are made with our quality riser less mounting bungs that look awesome in or on your top trees.

(custom handlebar orders are normally completed in 10 days or less)
